glòhng\'\'|praying mantis}} or {{tt|蘭花螳螂 \'\'làahnfā tòhnglòhng\'\'|orchid mantis}}\n|ru=Лурантис \'\'Lurantis\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name}}\n{{-}}\n\n==Related articles==\t\n* [[Totem Pokémon]]\n\n==Notes==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Grass}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Grass|prevnum=753|prev=Fomantis|nextnum=755|next=Morelull}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Mantidea]]\n[[es:Lurantis]]\n[[fr:Floramantis]]\n[[it:Lurantis]]\n[[ja:ラランテス]]\n[[zh:兰螳花]]'}